      - Maximum size: 1 MB,
      - Time played: 3 minutes, but the song can be longer,
      - Allowed format: MOD,
      - Please make sure, that the machine you want us to play your
        song with, appears on the disk (Amiga or PC),
      - On the PC we will use Fast Tracker,
      - One musician can compete with only one song.

        þ 8K Music Compo:       (original Rage competition)

