        þ WOP Compo [Winner Of the Party]: (Original SCEneST/Rage competition)
        
      - From now on we would like to award this prize to the best group of
        the party. Every group that competes at the party with anything
        (and didn't forget to put his/her groupname in the FILE_ID.DIZ)
        automatically enters this compo. The winners of every compo will
        get some points (see the table below), and the group with the most
        points at the end of the party will be the titled with the highest
        award of the party: "The group of the party" award. The winner will
        recieve some sort of prize, but the appreciation is the most impor-
        tant thing. The goal of the compo is to see groups compete in not
        just one or two competitions, but to compete in everything, and to
        contribute high quality productions. From now on, not only will the
        skill of the coders be the most important, but also how good your
        sense of humor is (Fun Compo, Lamer Demo Compo), because this is
        also very important to become the best group on the scene. The
        competitions of course will not be weighed with equal strength
        (like the winner of the demo compo will not recieve the same ammount
        of points as the third placed song in the music compo.) People
        competing in the name of several groups will only earn points for
        the first group mentioned in the FILE_ID.DIZ.


